,Recommended,288220,16857472,"Posted: 3 July, 2015",all,Kitteh,"Don't let the price fool you,  it's insanely worth it if you are looking for a visual novel that is so story packed.  It's well thoughtout,  and the storylines are simply amazing.  It's not your average visual novel however,  this is taking you through an entire year of life through Sian's eyes.  there are four men within the story that you can build relationships with,  one of them you already have a backstory with,  the other three you do not.  As the year progresses you will learn that keeping in contact with these men is vital,  but also impressing them is twice as important.   The game comes with a feature where you can dress Sian in certain outfits for each season that passes by the year.   If you get a correct combination,  the man you are trying to impress,  or a man in general who you haven't tried to impress may compliment you on that outfit.  The other way is perhaps waiting for certain holidays to come by,  buying them things you think they would enjoy would be best so pay attention to what these men tell you.  You may even be invited to certain events with them if you play your cards correctly.  This will build up hearts in the statistics section when you reach the weekend.There are other cute activities that you can do,  such as checking the message boards,  or checking your email for jobs to earn some of that extra cash.  All in the way to describe this game is you will not have a dull moment,  and you will not believe that it's an entire year of a makeup artists life."
